 Then I started to feel terrified. 

00:02:34.164 --> 00:02:35.382
 So I said, "Where are you?" 

00:02:35.386 --> 00:02:38.104
 I don’t know how to think, but I think if we use the mail service 

00:02:38.104 --> 00:02:39.422
 It must be registered 

