 He said, "It won't be easy to convince my company 

00:02:45.127 --> 00:02:46.837
 By shipping a large amount. " 

00:02:46.861 --> 00:02:49.389
 I said, "Solomon, I totally agree. 

00:02:49.413 --> 00:02:52.859
 I am in the process of developing an illustration, to take it with you to the board meeting. 

00:02:52.883 --> 00:02:54.063
 wait." 

