00:03:25.598 --> 00:03:27.384
 (Laughter) 

00:03:27.408 --> 00:03:29.789
 We are ready to ship as much gold as possible. " 

00:03:30.254 --> 00:03:32.495
 There is always a moment when your heart sings with joy, 

00:03:32.519 --> 00:03:34.301
 This was Solomon. 

00:03:34.325 --> 00:03:36.572
 He said, "I would be very happy if the deal was made successfully, 

00:03:36.586 --> 00:03:38.661
 Because I will get a good commission, too. ” 

00:03:38.685 --> 00:03:41.729
 So I said, "This is awesome. What will your share be spent?" 

00:03:42.363 --> 00:03:44.983
 He said, "On the property, what about you?" 

00:03:46.133 --> 00:03:49.180
 I thought about it long. 

00:03:50.625 --> 00:03:52.174
 So I said, "One word, 

00:03:53.632 --> 00:03:54.783
 chickpeas." 

00:03:54.807 --> 00:03:57.988
 (Laughter) 

