 I didn't know what to say! 

00:04:27.643 --> 00:04:30.530
 So I said, "Good evening, gold medal, good evening." 

00:04:30.554 --> 00:04:32.855
 (Laughter) 

00:04:33.323 --> 00:04:35.575
 Guys, you have to be aware that this went on, for weeks, 

00:04:35.609 --> 00:04:37.864
 And if so far, the best weeks of my life, 

00:04:37.864 --> 00:04:39.265
 I had to end up. 

00:04:39.265 --> 00:04:40.769
 Because he started getting out of control a little. 

00:04:40.769 --> 00:04:43.695
 My friends used to say, "James, do you want to come with us to have a drink?" 

00:04:43.695 --> 00:04:46.881
 I replied, "I can't. I'm waiting for an email on some gold." 

00:04:46.895 --> 00:04:48.513
 So I realized I had to end it. 

00:04:48.513 --> 00:04:50.043
 I had to take a trivial end. 

00:04:50.043 --> 00:04:51.319
 So I designed a plan. 

00:04:51.319 --> 00:04:54.655
 And I said, "Solomon, I'm worried about security. 

00:04:54.655 --> 00:04:56.426
 When we write to each other, 

00:04:56.426 --> 00:04:58.027
 We have to use symbols. " 

00:05:00.582 --> 00:05:01.733
 He agreed. 

00:05:01.757 --> 00:05:03.145
 (Laughter) 

00:05:03.169 --> 00:05:05.578
 I said, "Solomon, I spent a whole night finding this symbol 

00:05:05.872 --> 00:05:07.917
 We must use it in all of our next correspondence: 

00:05:08.001 --> 00:05:11.954
 Attorney: The rubber bear. 

00:05:13.564 --> 00:05:14.983
 Bank: scrambled eggs 

00:05:15.682 --> 00:05:18.249
 Legal: Ordered Coca Cola Bottle: M &amp; M's Chocolate 

