 Western Union: the huge rubber orchid. 

00:05:22.305 --> 00:05:24.137
 (Laughter) 

00:05:24.232 --> 00:05:26.993
 I know these are all the words they use, right? 

00:05:27.052 --> 00:05:30.637
 I said, "Please call me" Kit Kat "in all of our next correspondence. 

00:05:30.661 --> 00:05:34.724
 (Laughter) 

