 Then I received a message from him. 

00:05:52.968 --> 00:05:55.282
 He said, "The work is going on, and I try to etc etc etc ..." 

00:05:55.282 --> 00:05:58.280
 I said, "Man, you have to use the symbol!" 

00:06:01.478 --> 00:06:04.066
 What followed was the greatest message I ever received. 

00:06:04.090 --> 00:06:06.272
 (Laughter) 

00:06:07.675 --> 00:06:10.221
 I'm not kidding, that's what I got on my mailbox. 

00:06:10.939 --> 00:06:12.089
 It was a wonderful day. 

00:06:13.224 --> 00:06:14.375
 "The work is still going on. 

