 So that M &amp; M's can get started. 

00:06:32.118 --> 00:06:33.497
 (Laughter) 

00:06:33.940 --> 00:06:36.069
 Send out £ 1500 

00:06:36.093 --> 00:06:41.952
 Across the giant rubber lizard. " 

00:06:41.952 --> 00:06:45.275
 (clap) 

00:06:49.392 --> 00:06:51.797
 That was so funny, right, 

00:06:51.821 --> 00:06:53.171
 Which made me think: 

00:06:53.195 --> 00:06:56.106
 What will happen if you spend as much time as possible? 

00:06:56.130 --> 00:06:58.224
 In response to these messages as best I can? 

00:07:00.145 --> 00:07:03.121
 This is what I was doing 

00:07:03.145 --> 00:07:05.245
 For 3 years 

00:07:05.269 --> 00:07:06.550
 On your behalf. 

00:07:06.574 --> 00:07:08.969
 (Laughter) 

